The paper focuses on continual learning in the context of visual classification tasks, which suggests that it could fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the use of neural masking and dynamic network expansion mechanisms suggests a focus on neural networks and their architecture, which could place the paper in the categories of neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) and computational linguistics (cs.CL).
